data.description: This 42 acre horse property has it all. Zoned agricultural, with no covenants, a 50x70 drive through shop with overhead doors, 18x60 lean-to with 5 stalls and 4 horse runs, and a 140x210 riding arena, everything you need is ready to go. The 5 bedroom home features a main floor primary bedroom with 5 piece bath, a downstairs wet bar for entertaining, and a theater. The 2 car garage has an attached 30x30 heated workshop. With a 25kw solar system your utility bills will be substantially lower.
